bill.title: To designate a portion of United States Route 80 in Alabama as the "John R. Lewis Voting Rights Highway", and for other purposes.
bill.description: Designates the portion of U.S. Route 80 from Selma, Alabama to Montgomery, Alabama as the John R. Lewis Voting Rights Highway.

history.action: Referred to the House Committee on Transportation and Infrastructure.
